/*
 * This Hyperlambda snippet converts a large integer into its word representation,
 * effectively transforming numeric values into a more human-readable format.
 *
 * 1. [int2words]
 *    * Takes a signed 64-bit integer as input.
 *    * Converts the integer value 1200050 into its corresponding word form.
 *    * The output will be "one million two hundred thousand and fifty".
 */
int2words:1200050